attributes.title: Compass Problems
attributes.caption: Follow the compass or follow the sun? At this rate, the Achievement Hunter crew is going to die at sea.
attributes.description: The Achievement Hunter boys have voyaged far out to sea and have gotten very, very lost. Their only hope of finding dry land is following the compass back to shore. Too bad none of them know how to use a compass.
